{"tid":2505713,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人心中最佳紀錄短片\"DO NOT SPLIT\"","createTime":"2021-04-26T23:34:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T23:35:40.000Z","uid":228580,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"43f93009afa56fc5ba58766172d889bb1f2e2359","tid":2505713,"uid":228580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T23:34:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AndThenHK/photos/a.171398354346670/305333560953148/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FAndThenHK%2Fphotos%2Fa.171398354346670%2F305333560953148%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B60UPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=064d620e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/AndThenHK/photos/a.171398354346670/305333560953148/?type=3</a>"},{"pid":"8f9a6c715669d6fe7c88f2e4fcc50c2d349a595b","tid":2505713,"uid":228580,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"43f93009afa56fc5ba58766172d889bb1f2e2359","tid":2505713,"uid":228580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T23:34:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AndThenHK/photos/a.171398354346670/305333560953148/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FAndThenHK%2Fphotos%2Fa.171398354346670%2F305333560953148%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B60UPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=064d620e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/AndThenHK/photos/a.171398354346670/305333560953148/?type=3</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T23:34:58.000Z","msg":"｜#自己入圍紀錄片自己撐｜<br />\n第93屆 #奧斯卡金像獎頒獎典禮 於香港時間4月26日在洛杉磯舉行，挪威導演 Anders Hammer 執導的香港反送中運動紀錄片《Do Not Split》（#不割席）入選最佳紀錄短片五強，最終失落於講述納粹集中營的《Colette》，不過此片對香港人來說仍然意義重大。（詳盡得獎名單及國際線上關注香港的發言：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/3xrnFhB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3xrnFhB&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B60UPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=63413e15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/3xrnFhB</a>）<br />\n<br />\n《Do Not Split》片長35分鐘，紀錄了過去兩年社會上許多具標誌性的事件，當中包括2019年的「中大保衛戰」、「理大圍城」，以及2020年「港區國安法」通過等畫面，更有現場示威者和學生的訪問片段。<br />\n<br />\n身為挪威人，導演曾向外媒表示《Do Not Split》是他首次在香港拍攝的影片。他認為，反送中運動是2019年尤為重要的世界政治事件之一；眼見香港面臨民主價值挑戰，訴求至今更仍未能達成，他便決定嘗試從街頭的角度，呈現事情的真相。<br />\n<br />\n另外值得留意的是，香港各家電視台均不會播放奧斯卡頒獎禮，是香港52年以來，首次停播這項電影界盛事。大家現可於美國紀錄片製作公司 Field of Vision 的官方網站或 YouTube 上，免費觀看《Do Not Split》足本影片。<br />\n<br />\n《Do Not Split》<br />\n📲官方網站連結：<a href=\"http://fieldofvision.org/do-not-split\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffieldofvision.org%2Fdo-not-split&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B60UPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=1770d9e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">fieldofvision.org/do-not-split</a><br />\n📲YouTube連結：youtu.be/BpS-Y7ndNeQ<br />\n<br />\n【其他文章推薦】<br />\n專訪Golden Scene曾麗芬：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Pvh4Bu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Pvh4Bu&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B60UPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=ccedf3f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2Pvh4Bu</a><br />\n西營盤《二次人生》劇照展覽：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/3nf5PK1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3nf5PK1&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B60UPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=e505c793\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/3nf5PK1</a><br />\n<br />\n#AndThenHK跟住去 #和你一起 #好好過活 #DoNotSplit <br />\n💛FOLLOW <a href=\"http://AndThen.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FAndThen.hk&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B60UPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=6deefd5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">AndThen.hk</a><br />\n📘Facebook: <a href=\"http://AndThen.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FAndThen.hk&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B60UPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=6deefd5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">AndThen.hk</a><br />\n📷Instagram: <a href=\"http://instagram.com/andthenhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fandthenhk&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B60UPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=fb522f86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">instagram.com/andthenhk</a><br /